      "content": "i get that it's subjective, but for my readers i need something more concrete. if someone is flying into a major international business hub—like London, NYC, or Singapore—is there basically a baseline standard of \"sophistication\" they should follow to make sure they aren't seen as unprofessional? like, what does a standard high-class professional outfit or communication style look like globally?",
